@startuml System Overview

title Smart Rental System - Use Case Overview

' Actors
actor "Admin" as Admin
actor "Tenant" as Tenant

' System Boundary
rectangle "Smart Rental Backend System" {

  usecase "Authentication\n(6 use cases)" as Auth
  usecase "Building Management\n(5 use cases)" as Building
  usecase "Room Management\n(8 use cases)" as Room
  usecase "Tenant Management\n(6 use cases)" as TenantMgmt
  usecase "Contract Management\n(8 use cases)" as Contract
  usecase "Service Management\n(5 use cases)" as Service
  usecase "Meter Reading\n(9 use cases)" as Reading
  usecase "Invoice Management\n(14 use cases)" as Invoice
  usecase "Transaction Management\n(4 use cases)" as Transaction
  usecase "Issue Management\n(5 use cases)" as Issue

}

' Admin has access to all modules
Admin --> Auth
Admin --> Building
Admin --> Room
Admin --> TenantMgmt
Admin --> Contract
Admin --> Service
Admin --> Reading
Admin --> Invoice
Admin --> Transaction
Admin --> Issue

' Tenant has limited access
Tenant --> Auth
Tenant -[dotted]-> Invoice : "View Public Only"

note right of Admin
  Full system access
  All CRUD operations
  54+ use cases
end note

note right of Tenant
  Limited access
  - Login/Register
  - View own invoices
  3 use cases total
end note

note bottom of Invoice
  Most complex module:
  - Preview & Generate
  - Multi-payment
  - Bulk operations
  - Public access
end note

@enduml
